    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and is being sold with full transparency regarding its age and wear. The exterior has several noticeable scratches, some minor paint oxidation on the hood, and a few small door dings consistent with daily use. Inside, the upholstery shows significant wear, including a small tear in the driver's seat and some staining on the rear carpets. Mechanically, the car starts and runs, but it will likely need suspension work and a brake service in the near future. It is a solid candidate for someone willing to put in a little work, but it is being sold as-is.",
      "price": 19500.0,
