    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition, presenting exactly as it did when it first left the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep, mirror-like shine, and there are no chips, scratches, or imperfections to be found anywhere on the body. Inside, the cabin is pristine; the leather remains supple and free of wear, and all electronic features function perfectly. Mechanically, the car is beyond reproach, having been meticulously maintained with a full service history and stored in a climate-controlled environment. This is a rare opportunity to own a vehicle that has been preserved in showroom state, offering the next owner a truly like-new driving experience.",
      "price": 49000.0,
