    {
      "id": "sybil_0_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "sybil_0",
      "description": "We are pleased to present this impeccably preserved vehicle, maintained to the highest standards of automotive excellence. This example remains in showroom condition, exhibiting no discernible wear and reflecting a history of meticulous stewardship. From its flawless exterior finish to the pristine interior cabin, every detail confirms its status as a premier acquisition for the discerning enthusiast. Opportunities to secure a specimen of this caliber are exceedingly rare.",
